        "description": "Creates or updates assignment rows by unique key (user, project, capability, date). Dates are automatically normalized to Sunday (start of week). When capabilityId is omitted, it is auto-resolved from existing data if the user has exactly one capability on the project. Returns 400 if the user has multiple capabilities and none is specified.",
